                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep3-doctrine/show-404.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>We have a list page! Heck, we have a show page. Let's link them together.</p>
<p>First, the poor show route is nameless. Give it a name - and a new reason to live -
with <code>name="genus_show"</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="4b7af6f602">
