</p>
<p>That sounds good.</p>
<p>In the list template, and the <code>a</code> tag and use the <code>path()</code> function to point this
to the <code>genus_show</code> route. Remember - this route has a <code>{genusName}</code> wildcard, so
we <em>must</em> pass a value for that here. Add a set of curly-braces to make an array...
But this is getting a little long: so break onto multiple lines. Much better. Finish
with <code>genusName: genus.name</code>. And make sure the text is still <code>genus.name</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="0e55b0bb5e">
