<p>Then, <code>$genus = $em-&gt;getRepository()</code> with the <code>AppBundle:Genus</code> shortcut.
Ok now, is there a method that can help us? Ah, how about <code>findOneBy()</code>. This
works by passing it an array of things to find by - in our case <code>'name' =&gt; $genusName</code>:</p>
