</p>
<p>In the <code>prod</code> environment, this would be a 500 page. We do <em>not</em> want that - we want
the user to see a nice 404 page, ideally with something really funny on it.</p>
<p>Back in the controller, the <code>findOneBy()</code> method will either return <em>one</em> Genus object
or null. If it does <em>not</em> return an object, throw <code>$this-&gt;createNotFoundException('No genus found')</code>:</p>
