<p>Oh, and that message will only be shown to developers - not to end-users.</p>
<p>Head back, refresh, and <em>this</em> is a 404. In the <code>prod</code> environment, the user
will see a 404 template that you need to setup. I won't cover how to customize the
template here - it's pretty easy - just make sure it's really clever, and send me
a screenshot. Do it!</p>

    
